                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su"
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A nihili generates a field of gravity that functions in a 5-foot aura around itself (including 5 feet above the nihili), exerting a downward force toward the nihili\u2019s feet. This allows the nihili to function as if constantly under the effect of <i>spider climb</i>. Any creature entering this aura from an area of zero-g must succeed at a DC 15 Reflex saving throw or be knocked prone.",
